<!-- /wp:paragraph -->

<!-- wp:paragraph -->
<p>Another important consideration is the inclusion of specialized lockers for different sports. For example, football lockers should be large enough to accommodate the players' pads and helmets, while hockey lockers should have enough space for skates and sticks. A hockey stick rack can also be a useful addition, as it keeps the sticks organized and out of the way.</p>
